_sText:
This is a map I created from my rush_neighbourhood map for use in Hide n seek. It was created with the sole purpose of repopulating our hide n seek server with some fresh maps.

It is based in a neighbourhood map and any of you Australians will recognize the iconic hardware brand.

There are plenty of places to hide and I have also linked a prop list you can use as well.

[Prop List - Click Here](http://dumptext.com/knNtFgIS "Prop List")

Enjoy
